      "value": "During a Benefit Payment Period and while you reside in an Assisted Living Facility, we will pay a benefit for each day of Nursing Home Care you receive.\n\nPayment will be the actual daily Assisted Living Facility charges you incur, up to the Assisted Living Facility Daily Benefit. Your Assisted Living Facility Daily Benefit is shown on the Benefit Schedule. Benefits paid are subtracted from the Benefit Amount for Facility Care.",
