      "id": "f4",
      "name": "Bed Reservation Benefit",
      "value": "During a Benefit Payment Period, we will pay you a Bed Reservation Benefit if you:\n\n• are confined in a Nursing Home or reside in an Assisted Living Facility; and\n• become hospitalized; and\n• are billed by the Nursing Home or Assisted Living Facility to reserve your accommodations.\n\nPayment will be the actual daily Nursing Home or Assisted Living Facility charges you incur, up to the Nursing Home Daily Benefit or Assisted Living Facility Daily Benefit, as appropriate. The Daily Benefits are shown on the Benefit Schedule. Benefits paid are subtracted from the Benefit Amount for Facility Care. This benefit is payable for a maximum of 21 days per calendar year.",
      "confidence": 0.8,
      "sourceType": "ocr",
      "bbox": {
        "x": 58,
        "y": 600,
        "width": 676,
        "height": 200
      }
